citations:
    citation-agot-tyrion-i:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Tyrion I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Tyrion. Bran lies comatose from his fall. Tyrion is reading in the Winterfell library. He speaks to Joffrey and Sandor Clegane in the yard, slapping Joffrey twice and ordering him to offer condolences to Ned and Catelyn. Tyrion announces he intends to accompany Benjen Stark and Jon Snow north to the Wall. Key dialogue: Tyrion says 'Death is so terribly final, while life is full of possibilities.'"
